      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6 14c-1 2-3 1-3 2s2 1 3 2 1 3 6 3 5-2 6-3 3-1 3-2-2 0-3-2c0-1 1-2 1-4 0-3-2-6-7-6s-7 3-7 6c0 2 1 3 1 4Z"/></svg>
